value: Breeds in northeastern Siberia at Cape Serdze, Kooshka and Providence Bay, perhaps also on the shores of the Sea of, Okhotsk,^ and in north- western Alaska at Wainwright, Cape Prince of Wales and possibly at Nome. Migrates through eastern Siberia, Kamchatka and the Commander Islands and winters from China and Japan south to Burma, the Andaman and Nicobar Islands, Philippines, and Malay Archipelago to Australia.
